yle="margin:0px 5px 5px 0px" title="Yammer logo new"&gt;&lt;/a&gt; TECH CRUNCH - Sep 27 - &lt;a href="http://www.yammer.com"&gt;Yammer&lt;/a&gt;, an enterprise social network and  communications platform, has raised $17M in new funding led by The  Social+Capital Partnership, a new fund established by former Facebook VP  Chamath Palihapitiya. Previous investors Charles River Ventures,  Emergence Capital and U.S. Venture Partners also participated in the  round. Palihapitiya will have an observer’s seat on Yammer’s board of  directors. This brings Yammer’s total financing to $57M.&lt;/p&gt;&#xd;
&lt;p&gt;by &lt;a href="http://www.linkedin.com/pub/leena-rao/7/428/212"&gt;Leena Rao&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="http://techcrunch.com/2011/09/27/former-facebook-vp-chamath-palihapitiya-leads-17m-round-in-enterprise-social-networking-platform-yammer/"&gt;See full article at Tech Crunch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xd;
